<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Upload Center - Intentionally Vulnerable Lab</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="ivl-body">
  <a class="ivl-skip-link" href="#ivl-main">Skip to main content</a>
  <div class="ivl-shell">
    <header class="ivl-header">
      <div class="ivl-header-inner">
        <a class="ivl-brand" href="/">
          <img src="/public/assets/logo.svg" alt="Intentionally Vulnerable Lab logo">
          <span>Intentionally Vulnerable Lab</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="ivl-nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <ul class="ivl-nav-list">
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/comments">Comments</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/orders/1">Orders</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/upload">Upload</a></li>
          </ul>
          <button type="button" class="ivl-theme-toggle" data-ivl-theme-toggle aria-pressed="false">
            <span class="ivl-theme-toggle__icon" data-ivl-theme-icon><img src="/public/assets/icon-moon.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="ivl-theme-toggle__label" data-ivl-theme-label>Dark mode</span>
          </button>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="ivl-main" id="ivl-main">
      <section class="ivl-card ivl-stack" aria-labelledby="ivl-upload-title">
        <div>
          <h1 class="ivl-heading-xl" id="ivl-upload-title">Upload anything</h1>
          <p class="ivl-muted">Multer accepts every file type and keeps original filenames, and the optional executor happily runs `.js` payloads. Lab only chaos; embrace it.</p>
        </div>
        <% if (error) { %>
          <p class="ivl-status ivl-status--error" role="alert"><%= error %></p>
        <% } %>
        <% if (message) { %>
          <p class="ivl-status ivl-status--success" role="status"><%= message %></p>
        <% } %>
        <form class="ivl-form" method="POST" action="/upload" enctype="multipart/form-data">
          <div class="ivl-field">
            <label class="ivl-label" for="ivl-file-input">Choose file</label>
            <input class="ivl-file" type="file" id="ivl-file-input" name="file" required>
          </div>
          <div>
            <button class="ivl-button" type="submit">Upload file</button>
          </div>
        </form>
        <p>After uploading, hit <code class="ivl-mono">/uploads/exec?file=&lt;payload.js&gt;</code> to trigger evaluation.</p>
        <p class="ivl-muted">Uploaded files land in <code class="ivl-mono">public/uploads/</code>. Clean up manually if you need a fresh lab state.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="ivl-footer">RCE on demand - great for demo walk-throughs and defensive blue-team practice.</footer>
  </div>
  <script src="/public/app.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
